{"tid":527854,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Delta航空認證玻璃心？　官網直呼中國「瓷器」","createTime":"2018-01-13T06:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T17:13:02.000Z","uid":29552,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"acd1fd2cf4ddb92f093507e68275afb47009444a","tid":527854,"uid":29552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"中國官方近日進行一場「大掃除」，繼萬豪酒店把台灣、香港、澳門與西藏列為「國家」被中國當局盯上後，達美航空、美敦力藥廠和ZARA服務也被追殺，甚至紛紛加入「道歉大賽」。但有眼尖的網友發現，在今日的達美航空官網上，竟然直呼中國「瓷器」。<br />\n<br />\n記者在今日早上9時50分左右進入達美航空官網，在選擇「國家與語言」的欄目中，竟然出現了「中國(瓷器)」的選項，而在亞太地區的選項中，更是不見「中國」的蹤跡，反倒是看見了台灣、泰國、日本和「瓷器」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣批踢踢網友紛紛表示：「易碎阿，太貼切了。」、「這個翻譯太神。」、「做網站的是不是台灣人？一語雙關。」、「翻譯正確XD。」、「是現在進行式耶，達美航空真的很敢，支瓷到底。」、「翻譯正確，china是瓷器無誤。」、「真的是高級酸法。」、「超猛！」<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://zt.delta.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzt.delta.com%2F&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=afcb37fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://zt.delta.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180113/1277802/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180113%2F1277802%2F&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c8ad21ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180113%2F1277802%2F&h=3ed95c47\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180113/1277802/</a>"},{"pid":"d2d5791a7f1e7ce97f939b86c74f0798c967fb48","tid":527854,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3208a00f05ad086bb5b1e859baf67305f4bcc476","tid":527854,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"瓷器人 玻璃心 100% match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b1082b46d9ea76013b1af55573f7e9869c6f7c","tid":527854,"uid":39527,"li